column5: Got out again with the kiddies and managed 1 in about a half hour of fishing.
What a looker that fish is lol
I tried to wipe the mud off of it    I had to get my wife to wipe off my face for the pic. The little bugger threw mud EVERYWHERE
what was it doing, trying to tunnel through the bank when you caught it? Nice specimen though
pretty well lol  the first few feet of water is pure mud
